description:
With Earth no longer able to sustain life, huge artificial satellites called &quot;near-orbitals&quot;were constructed for people to live on. To protect themselves, the near-orbitals banded together to form N.O.V.A., the Near Orbit Vanguard Alliance. Now, a strange threat has emerged from the darkness of space. A Marine ship, reported missing just a week ago, has suddenly reappeared and is headed directly for the near-orbitals, ignoring all communications. Against his will, retired Marine hero Kal Wardin is forcefully returned to active duty to prevent mankind's annihilation. 

The emulator is Xbox360 controller compatible.

System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.
nVidia GeForce GT 620 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.
3 Gig of ram or more.
Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.

Game emulates very well, and I have mapped the turn buttons to the right analog stick (Xbox360 controller), you can clear and re-map however you want.

Read the README!! text file.

